author: julianfoad
msg: * STATUS: Follow up to r8839, issue 1756.

author: julianfoad
msg: Never "repair" inconsistent EOL style during an import.  Part of issue 1756.
Inconsistent EOL style when svn:eol-style is set will now result in failure,
just as it would during a commit.
(send_file_contents): Do not request repair of inconsistent line endings.

author: julianfoad
msg: Reduce memory usage of multiple-target commits (part of issue 1635).
(svn_client_commit): Use a subpool in the target-processing loop.
